lead_paragraph: Chris Davis' RBI double broke a seventh-inning tie, Manny Machado went 4 for 5 and the Baltimore Orioles ended a four-game losing streak with a 6-4 victory over the Cleveland Indians on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Davis, Machado Lead Orioles to 6-4 Win Over Indians
